"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-team-usa-ends-nigeria-historic-run-advances-paris-olympics-semifinals\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Wednesday marked the beginning of the elimination round for women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099sOlympic basketballin Paris, and the US earned the top overall seed.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 95, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997598934, \"rank\": 2.4016523468269003e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995819590332, \"rank\": 4.1498092132267496e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They drew\\u00c2the Cinderella team\\u00c2of the tournament in the quarterfinals \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Nigeria.\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinderella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4360586521177892e-29, \"text\": \"Cinderella\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinderella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinderella\"}, {\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9624438927997488, \"rank\": 0.03804389228087575, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a chance to make history, the Nigerian team took the court against the gold standard of women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hoops.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5940977561132319, \"rank\": 0.6823883510136293, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although they did not prevail, they put up a fight, and their run was both inspirational and a disclaimer \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 African women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s basketball has arrived.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s no secret that the American team has come out sluggishly in each of its three group phase games.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.8580551969036366, \"rank\": 0.16517523626847117, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had the same starting lineup in each of those games, so coach Cheryl Reeve opted to make a change.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cheryl Reeve\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She inserted Jackie Young into the starting lineup for Diana Taurasi, a move likely made in part due to Young\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s defensive acumen.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.9863866062973025, \"rank\": 0.013801035077630006, \"text\": \"Jackie Young\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Diana Taurasi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her matchup was star scorer Ezinne Kalu, who needed to be kept in check if the US wanted to separate in the game.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezinne_Kalu\", \"score\": 0.999999997555733, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ezinne Kalu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezinne_Kalu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezinne_Kalu\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995819590332, \"rank\": 4.1498092132267496e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means that three Aces players were in the starting lineup.\\u00c2  After A\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ja Wilson scored a bucket on the opening possession, the game hit a bit of a standstill.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chelsea Gray missed yet another open jump shot, as she is yet to make a basket outside of the paint in this Olympics.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chelsea Gray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kalu had trouble getting going as well, in large part due to Young\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s stifling defense.\\u00c2  After three minutes, the score was knotted up at 2-2 until Gray found Breanna Stewart for a basket to break the dry spell.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Breanna Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Young missed her first attempt of the game but Wilson came up with a big offensive rebound that led to a US bucket.\\u00c2  Then, Jackie Young started cooking again.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995819590332, \"rank\": 4.1498092132267496e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.9863866062973025, \"rank\": 0.013801035077630006, \"text\": \"Jackie Young\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After an uncharacteristic turnover, she got the ball back for Team USA and scored on two straight possessions: one on a step-through in the paint, the other a mid-range pullup.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999834321899, \"rank\": 1.5534818616007885e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did her thing on the defensive end too, causing three turnovers for Nigeria.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9624438927997488, \"rank\": 0.03804389228087575, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigeria hung tough though, down only four toward the end of the first quarter.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9624438927997488, \"rank\": 0.03804389228087575, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brittney Griner gave them all they could handle though, blocking and altering every shot within a ten-foot radius of the rim, and catching high-lows for easy US buckets.\\u00c2  A flurry of buckets by Team USA pushed the lead to 12 at one point, and they clung to a nine-point lead at the end of the first quarter.\\u00c2  After a long stretch to begin the period without any Aces players on the floor, A\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ja Wilson and Kelsey Plum checked into the game, with the US only up four.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brittney Griner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\"}, {\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995819590332, \"rank\": 4.1498092132267496e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2128, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999834321899, \"rank\": 1.5534818616007885e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelsey_Plum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelsey Plum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelsey_Plum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelsey_Plum\"}, {\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995819590332, \"rank\": 4.1498092132267496e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Things exploded from here.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099  Plum found Wilson for an easy midrange jumper, the first of her back to back buckets.\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jackie Young checked back into the game, and the team really started to roll.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.9863866062973025, \"rank\": 0.013801035077630006, \"text\": \"Jackie Young\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plum connected on a step back 3 to push the lead further, and on the following possession, Young hustled for an offensive rebound and passed it to Plum, who found Wilson for another bucket.\\u00c2  Young grabbed another offensive board and was fouled on her putback attempt, but she made both free throws.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She followed that up with a midrange pullup, and Wilson scored on the next possession to push the lead to 15.\\u00c2  Wilson had a blocked shot and Young caused a turnover, finding Stewart for a fastbreak layup, giving the team a 52-33 halftime lead.\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 3144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2949, \"end\": 2955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 3012, \"end\": 3018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 3075, \"end\": 3082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.634414762140122e-36, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second half began in a similar fashion to the way it ended: Jackie Young making a jump shot.\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3210, \"end\": 3222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.9863866062973025, \"rank\": 0.013801035077630006, \"text\": \"Jackie Young\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Young_(basketball)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilson continued to run the floor well and get easy buckets, and the lead ballooned to 25.\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3243, \"end\": 3249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.70943242996249e-24, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, Nigeria stopped the bleeding with a 3-pointer, but not before the US put together a 10-0 run.\\u00c2  Gray, despite her scoring struggles, had a series of head spinning passes that left viewers in awe.\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3343, \"end\": 3350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_foo